Package: drhutools
Type: Package
Title: Toolbox for Writing an Academic Paper of Empirical Research with Rmarkdown
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yue", "Hu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "yuehu@tsinghua.edu.cn")
Maintainer: Yue Hu <yuehu@tsinghua.edu.cn>
Description: A toolbox for conducting empirical research with rmarkdown and its extensions. The package includes tools for data analyses, visualization, and documenting.
